{"tid":1070990,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"被勝利害慘！ YG明舉行股東大會撤換梁鉉錫代表製作人一職","createTime":"2019-03-21T04:47:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-21T22:50:32.000Z","uid":74065,"like":19,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"585bfefa26235f610b3153c3a9554936ee128b6c","tid":1070990,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T04:47:19.000Z","msg":"被勝利害慘！ YG明舉行股東大會撤換梁鉉錫代表製作人一職<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3376/3376056.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3376%2F3376056.jpg&h=8586d0f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲ YG創始人梁鉉錫。（圖／CFP）<br />\n<br />\n勝利涉及性招待、偷拍群組事件，讓前經紀公司<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>YG娛樂（YG Entertainment）股價下跌近30％，YG也將在明（22）日舉行股東大會，計畫撤換梁鉉錫（楊</strong></span>賢碩）代表製作人的職位。<br />\n<br />\n據《韓國先驅報》報導，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>YG已安排本週五（3/22）舉行股東大會，決定是否更換代表製作人梁鉉錫及其弟弟兼首席執行長梁敏錫，這是由於公司近期圍繞勝利性賄賂和腐敗醜聞。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n梁鉉錫身為YG的創始人兼代表製作人，手上持有公司16.12％的股份，而他的兄弟楊敏碩則持有該公司股票的3.31％。<br />\n<br />\n自勝利事件爆發開始，YG的股價至今已經下跌近30％，雖然勝利否認了所有不法行為的指控，但宣布從團隊BigBang中退出，也終止了與YG的合約；YG公司也曾發表聲明，對旗下藝人的管理鬆懈表示抱歉。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，除了勝利之外，YG旗下藝人負面新聞不斷，讓粉絲呼籲YG最重要的是要改變領導階層。<br />\n<br />\n在本週股東大會召開之前，現在正在關注主要的機構投資者，他們的投票將決定YG的命運。有義務披露其持股比例超過5％的投資者，包括持股9.53％的Global World Music Investment 、8.5％的Naver、7.54％的Shanghai Fengying Business Consultant Partnership和6.06％的韓國國家養老金服務。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"489d7757e811d4805fc91c9912937ae2a9f644fa","tid":1070990,"uid":182846,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T05:02:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0a1bd1d81ac497422a849c09ab919242f168d47e","tid":1070990,"uid":241764,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T05:07:54.000Z","msg":"勝利！勝利！勝利！"},{"pid":"0654988c10ba4a85c5b71cdd7c0ac833ac511b2d","tid":1070990,"uid":82018,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T05:43:45.000Z","msg":"創辦人先得個16%<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4108392275f7e13cf17089d636c734fe3e0a2bbd","tid":1070990,"uid":186997,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T06:10:48.000Z","msg":"犯罪集團頭目終於收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dbd51294d62cb57c1d8d7531e04f4644b978f29","tid":1070990,"uid":33907,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"4108392275f7e13cf17089d636c734fe3e0a2bbd","tid":1070990,"uid":186997,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T06:10:48.000Z","msg":"犯罪集團頭目終於收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T06:14:54.000Z","msg":"幕後大boss都未出場<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca8f41a61d68c8b5b5418ab6b2fa54265490e809","tid":1070990,"uid":10757,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T06:21:59.000Z","msg":"班官呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de1fc36eb714531357b62409f1bef3accd3ce1f4","tid":1070990,"uid":33077,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T06:26:09.000Z","msg":"做樣之嗎"},{"pid":"d0480d037dae63b6f506bb462f1d1fb0151cde06","tid":1070990,"uid":179051,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T08:47:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f12afdc93878c2eab7a2aba978c4cadcf7a63aa7","tid":1070990,"uid":89931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T08:56:37.000Z","msg":"YG<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ad77cff3ab1ef60e88ec82f3111e5089458be5c","tid":1070990,"uid":174767,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTi